      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exceptionally well-maintained vehicle, which stands as a testament to engineering longevity and consistent care. This unit has undergone a comprehensive assessment to ensure its mechanical reliability and structural integrity remain beyond reproach. Boasting a clean aesthetic and a smooth, responsive driving experience, this vehicle offers a sophisticated solution for the discerning driver who prioritizes both value and performance. This is a premier opportunity to acquire a dependable asset that has been preserved in commendable condition.",
      "price": 29850.0,
